org.eclipse.keyple.core.service.event

Class AbstractDefaultSelectionsRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.keyple.core.service.event.AbstractDefaultSelectionsRequest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultSelectionsRequest

    public abstract class AbstractDefaultSelectionsRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class defines the POJO used to carry the default selection request data.

    The default selection request is obtained from the selection preparation process and provided to an observable reader.

    Since:
    0.9
